            <title><![CDATA[[话筒]注意！#空调太脏女子回家就犯哮喘#近日，杭州的张女士一回家就哮喘发作，但家中并无过敏原。医生仔细问询后推断，可能和家中开空调有关。医生表示，未经清...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>注意！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E5%A4%AA%E8%84%8F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%B1%E7%8A%AF%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%E5%A4%AA%E8%84%8F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%9B%9E%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%B1%E7%8A%AF%E5%93%AE%E5%96%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#空调太脏女子回家就犯哮喘#</span></a><br><br>近日，杭州的张女士一回家就哮喘发作，但家中并无过敏原。医生仔细问询后推断，可能和家中开空调有关。<br><br>医生表示，未经清洗的空调内的真菌、细菌可能会飘落到人体的呼吸道，轻者造成真菌致病性哮喘，重者造成哮喘急性发作。按照医生嘱咐，张女士回家清洗了空调，当天哮喘就停止了发作。<br><br>那么问题来了，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85%E6%B8%85%E6%B4%81%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E7%A9%BA%E8%B0%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#你多久清洁一次空调#</span></a>？PS：又帮大家五一宅家找了项好运动，洗空调～<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6N93kJN" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
